Text: There's a peer who's up to 99.8% but got stuck and can't complete this torrent. I've had the same problem on two other torrents and have figured out that it's a corrupted text file. If you stop the torrent, do a "Force Re-check", then look in the files section, you will see the videos are at 100%, but one at 99%, though the complete video is there, uTorrent just stops because it can't go on to verify the text file. Just download the original text file i uploaded for you at the link below, stop the torrent in uTorrent, and replace the corrupt one in the folder. Now right click on the torrent and select "Force Re-Check" when complete start the torrent. (sometimes you need to remove (Not Delete) the torrent from uTorrent, then redownload it above which will do an automatic "Force Re-Check :)
just enter in "zshare" between the dots
and also rename the downloaded file just like the original because the file host i used added underslashes.
